      <title>摩根士丹利的斯利蒙认为股市将飙升至历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/morgan-stanley-s-slimmon-sees-stocks-soaring-beyond-record-highs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利(Morgan Stanley)的安德鲁·斯利蒙(Andrew Slimmon)表示，即使股市创下历史新高，投资者仍坚持持有现金，这表明市场有足够的空间扩大涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/morgan-stanley-s-slimmon-sees-stocks-soaring-beyond-record-highs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 20:56:07 GMT</pubDate>
